<th>
<h3>Hours</h3>
</th>
<td>100 Hours Minimum</td>
<td>150 Hours Minimum</td>
<td>Full-time throughout the semester</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>
<h3>Verification</h3>
</th>
<td>Pre-approval by the internship director <strong>recommended</strong>.&nbsp; Pre-approval required if admitted to COB for Fall 2008 or after.</td>
<td>Pre-approval required by the Internship Director before enrollment.<br /></td>
<td>Pre-approval required by Internship Director before enrollment.</td>
